  "title": "Restaurant Service Crew (5 Days)",
  "description": "<p>SKI is the up-and-coming restaurant in Tanjong Pagar, serving amazing food and providing fantastic service for the guests.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You can expect a 5-day work week with an amazing compensation structure that includes:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monthly Commission</li>\n  <li>Monthly Full Attendance Bonus</li>\n  <li>Annual Performance Bonus</li>\n  <li>Dine-in Discount</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job description</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet and serve customers with a positive attitude and genuine smile</li>\n  <li>Take and process orders accurately using the POS system</li>\n  <li>Provide recommendations and answer customer queries about the menu</li>\n  <li>Serve food and beverages promptly and efficiently</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the dining and service areas</li>\n  <li>Clear tables, reset seating areas, and manage table turnover during peak hours</li>\n  <li>Support the team with opening, closing, and shift change duties</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with food hygiene, safety, and cleanliness standards</li>\n  <li>Assist with other tasks as assigned by the supervisor or manager</li>\n</ul>",
